<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Hotel XYZ</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #424769;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #2d3250;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            width: calc(33.33% - 20px);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

            .feature-item:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

            .feature-item img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

        footer {
            background-color: #424769;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Hotel Olympia</h1>
        <p>Il tuo luogo ideale per il relax</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Servizi in Evidenza</h2>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578683010236-d716f9a3f461?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Camera di Lusso">
                    <h3>Camere di Lusso</h3>
                    <p>Esperienza di soggiorno di prima classe con le nostre camere di lusso.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1661879028525-978a222c0cc8?q=80&w=2071&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Ristorante Raffinato">
                    <h3>Ristorante Raffinato</h3>
                    <p>Gustate piatti deliziosi preparati dai nostri chef esperti.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529290130-4ca3753253ae?q=80&w=2076&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Spa e Benessere">
                    <h3>Spa e Benessere</h3>
                    <p>Rigenerate mente e corpo presso la nostra spa di lusso.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
